ited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip"}}}